---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="UAC 周刊 · 写作课程"
  description="每周四推送不被算法喜爱的文章，已有78+位同学加入。系统学习企业家式写作，用内容构建你的个人品牌。"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-badge">📬 每周四更新</span>
      <h1>UAC 周刊</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">不被算法喜爱的文章，写给认真思考的人</p>
      <div class="hero-price">
        <span class="price-tag">¥39</span>
        <span class="price-period">/ 三年</span>
      </div>
      <a href="#join" class="btn-primary btn-large">立即加入 →</a>
      <p class="hero-note">已有 <strong>78+</strong> 位同学加入</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Get -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">你会得到什么</h2>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">📰</div>
          <h3>每周精选文章</h3>
          <p>每周四推送一篇深度文章，涵盖写作方法论、个人品牌、内容变现。不追热点，只写经得起时间考验的内容。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">🎯</div>
          <h3>系统写作课程</h3>
          <p>从选题到发布的完整写作系统。不是碎片技巧，而是可复用的企业家式写作方法论。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">💬</div>
          <h3>专属交流群</h3>
          <p>与 78+ 位认真写作的同学一起交流。提问、讨论、互相反馈，不再一个人孤独写作。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">📚</div>
          <h3>独家内容库</h3>
          <p>过往所有周刊文章、写作模板、选题库。加入即可解锁，随时查阅。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="section section-accent">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="philosophy">
        <h2>独特且正确</h2>
        <p class="philosophy-lead">信息越泛滥，优质内容越稀缺。</p>
        <p>算法推荐的是"大多数人会点击的内容"，而不是"对你真正有价值的内容"。UAC 周刊反其道而行——不迎合算法，只服务真正想提升写作能力的少数人。</p>
        <p>每周一篇文章，像企业家做产品一样做内容：找到真实需求、打磨交付体验、建立长期信任。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Preview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">往期内容精选</h2>
      <div class="content-list">
        <div class="content-item">
          <span class="content-tag">写作方法论</span>
          <h3>如何像企业家一样写作</h3>
          <p>写作不是表达，而是产品。用 MVP 思维验证选题，用闭环思维持续迭代。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-item">
          <span class="content-tag">个人品牌</span>
          <h3>从 0 到 1 构建个人品牌</h3>
          <p>不是成为网红，而是成为某个领域值得信赖的声音。关键是持续输出 + 真实交付。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-item">
          <span class="content-tag">内容变现</span>
          <h3>第一个 100 块的闭环</h3>
          <p>不是靠流量分成，而是靠解决真实问题获得回报。七个步骤，每一步都是验证过的路径。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="section section-pricing" id="join">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h2>加入 UAC 周刊</h2>
        <div class="pricing-price">
          <span class="price-number">¥39</span>
          <span class="price-unit">/ 三年</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>✓ 每周一篇深度文章（持续三年）</li>
          <li>✓ 完整写作课程体系</li>
          <li>✓ 专属交流群</li>
          <li>✓ 过往所有内容库</li>
          <li>✓ 写作模板与工具包</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="btn-primary btn-large btn-full">立即加入</a>
        <p class="pricing-note">一次付费，三年服务。无自动续费，无隐藏消费。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">常见问题</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Q: 周刊更新频率？</h3>
          <p>A: 每周四推送一篇文章，节假日可能顺延。三年约 150+ 篇内容。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Q: 可以退款吗？</h3>
          <p>A: 加入后 7 天内不满意可全额退款，无需理由。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Q: 如何接收内容？</h3>
          <p>A: 通过微信群 + 邮件双通道推送，确保不会错过任何一期。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Q: 适合什么水平的人？</h3>
          <p>A: 适合所有想系统提升写作能力的人，无论你是刚开始还是已经有一定经验。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 100px 24px 80px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(245,80,0,0.04) 0%, transparent 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: rgba(245,80,0,0.1);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero-price { margin: 24px 0 28px; }
  .price-tag { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-accent); }
  .price-period { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
  .btn-large { padding: 14px 40px; font-size: 17px; border-radius: 10px; }
  .btn-full { display: block; text-align: center; }
  .hero-note { margin-top: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 28px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.88; }

  /* Section Common */
  .section { padding: 64px 24px; }
  .section-inner { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .section-accent { background: rgba(245,80,0,0.03); }

  /* Benefits Grid */
  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .benefit-card {
    padding: 28px;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .benefit-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .benefit-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .benefit-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .benefit-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* Philosophy */
  .philosophy { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .philosophy h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .philosophy-lead { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .philosophy p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.8; }

  /* Content List */
  .content-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
  .content-item {
    padding: 28px;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .content-item:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
  .content-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: rgba(245,80,0,0.08);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .content-item h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .content-item p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* Pricing */
  .section-pricing { background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(245,80,0,0.03) 100%); }
  .pricing-card {
    max-width: 440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pricing-card h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .pricing-price { margin: 24px 0; }
  .price-number { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-accent); }
  .price-unit { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
  .pricing-features { list-style: none; text-align: left; margin: 28px 0; padding: 0; }
  .pricing-features li { padding: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .pricing-features li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .pricing-note { margin-top: 16px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-text-secondary); }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-list { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .faq-item { padding: 24px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .faq-item p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pricing-card { padding: 28px 20px; }
  }
</style>